#: ../../../design_documents/ArrayDispatch.md:1
msgid "vtkArrayDispatch and Related Tools"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../design_documents/ArrayDispatch.md:3
msgid "Background"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../design_documents/ArrayDispatch.md:5
msgid ""
"VTK datasets store most of their important information in subclasses of "
"`vtkAbstractArray`. Vertex locations (`vtkPoints::Data`), cell topology "
"(`vtkCellArray::Offsets/Connectivity`), and numeric point, cell, and generic "
"attributes (`vtkFieldData::Data`) are the dataset features accessed most "
"frequently by VTK algorithms, and these all rely on the `vtkAbstractArray` "
"API."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../design_documents/ArrayDispatch.md:11
msgid "Terminology"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../design_documents/ArrayDispatch.md:13
msgid "This page uses the following terms:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../design_documents/ArrayDispatch.md:15
msgid ""
"An __ArrayType__ is a concrete subclass of `vtkAbstractArray`. For instance:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../design_documents/ArrayDispatch.md:17
msgid "`vtkAOSDataArrayTemplate<float>` or `vtkFloatArray`,"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../design_documents/ArrayDispatch.md:18
msgid "`vtkSOADataArrayTemplate<vtkTypeInt64>` or `vtkSOATypeInt64Array`,"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../design_documents/ArrayDispatch.md:19
msgid "`vtkConstantArray<vtkTypeInt8>` or `vtkConstantTypeInt8Array`,"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../design_documents/ArrayDispatch.md:20
msgid "`vtkStringArray`,"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../design_documents/ArrayDispatch.md:21
msgid "`vtkBitArray`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../design_documents/ArrayDispatch.md:23
msgid ""
"An __ArrayTypeTag__ is a constexpr integer value that represents an _class_ "
"of arrays which can be either templated or non-templated. For instance:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../design_documents/ArrayDispatch.md:26
msgid ""
"`vtkAOSDataArrayTemplate<float>` has an ArrayTypeTag of `std::"
"integral_constant<int, vtkArrayTypes::VTK_AOS_DATA_ARRAY>`,"
msgstr ""

