msgid ""
"`vtkSOADataArrayTemplate<vtkTypeInt64>` has an ArrayTypeTag of `std::"
"integral_constant<int, vtkArrayTypes::VTK_SOA_DATA_ARRAY>`,"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../design_documents/ArrayDispatch.md:30
msgid ""
"`vtkConstantArray<vtkTypeInt8>` has an ArrayTypeTag of `std::"
"integral_constant<int, vtkArrayTypes::VTK_CONSTANT_ARRAY>`,"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../design_documents/ArrayDispatch.md:32
msgid ""
"`vtkStringArray` has an ArrayTypeTag of `std::integral_constant<int, "
"vtkArrayTypes::VTK_STRING_ARRAY>`,"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../design_documents/ArrayDispatch.md:34
msgid ""
"`vtkBitArray` has an ArrayTypeTag of `std::integral_constant<int, "
